@CDCgov 2100+ COMPLETED COVID19 tests missing from Rockford IL test site. Tested there last Friday-told results in 48-72 hours. Then changed to 10-14 days. Now they’re gone?! The National Guard was there, for crying out loud! What are we to do? This is ludicrous. 
https://t.co/BiXvmUil64
